data.description: Attention Investors, Remodelers, DIYers! Come add this fabulous A frame home to your investment portfolio today. With a little sweaty equity come make this home shine once more in the attractive Holiday Hills community. This home sit on just over 1/2 acre with beautiful mature landscaping and terrtiorial views to the east. Plenty of storage options with 2 out buildings and covered patio as well! Put in your offers now before this one is gone! Property to be sold in As-Is Condition.
